Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.94,0:00:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能看見痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.05,0:00:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是空虛地渡過每一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.46,0:00:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在充滿消沉心情的城市裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.96,0:00:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你在優美地閃耀着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！\NCarry On！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.24,0:00:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要灰心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.34,0:00:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！\NShinin Oh！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.78,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被破壞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.35,0:00:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成愛啊，\N像把宇宙包裏一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.89,0:01:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.43,0:01:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.75,0:01:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在卡沙尼里亞聼到的鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在超高空飛舞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.22,0:01:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨大機動戰士所發出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.92,0:01:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，\N它像引胡索等人去宇宙般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.89,0:01:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索向媽媽的墳墓道別後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.53,0:01:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和連賀斯Jr\N一起向宇宙進發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.54,0:01:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸製造的戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍的支援真緩慢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.94,0:02:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擊毀敵機的話，那就是訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要發射偽裝嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把所有發射！\N我們會被擊中啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.65,0:02:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別一次過發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥還只是剛剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.82,0:02:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不穿太空衣沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為白色方舟\N不用深入敵陣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又發現熱源，\N一時，上方3度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人只是憑直覺攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我好性不穿太空衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.82,0:03:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一定要盡快消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.69,0:03:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雷射砲攻擊\N拉京的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一部持雷射砲的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他只不過是新型機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次來到宇宙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.11,0:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是甚麽雷射砲！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美愛娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之翼？V2！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.56,0:03:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是出動機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和本隊離開得太遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又聼到！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅！ 湯馬殊！\N要射來這裡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.54,0:04:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.01,0:04:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是正接近我們嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是方向和剛才的不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聼到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個鈴明顯是在引我過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像蜜蜂見蜜糖般過來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.77,0:04:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用斷頭台時\N一定要掛上的鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成[贊歷古] 的鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會和機動戰士\N動作的周波數聯動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.11,0:04:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我在腦内感到敵人的形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是白色傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.29,0:05:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要在這裡消滅他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後援機請用\NV2的翼作盾牌戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用翼的光作盾牌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.64,0:05:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我用它作盾牌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.77,0:05:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聼你說話做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對贊歷古的\N雷射砲感到吃驚時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們已步向死方啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.00,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.05,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無熱源反應，在遠距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方的損傷如何？知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.29,0:06:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩部被毀，兩部重傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機體識別呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，你救了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！\N美愛娜小姐和富蘭尼小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.07,0:06:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也打得好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說話那麽得體吧，細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，富蘭尼小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是因為\N和美麗的姐姐在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以很興奮罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.16,0:06:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰是美麗的姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答我啊，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.80,0:06:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你答我呢，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.38,0:06:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有命令叫我們去凱蘭特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那裡現在空無一人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.28,0:07:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是神聖軍事同盟的首領吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令是以占.撒哈林之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送來拉京的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和發出命令的\N也是占.撒哈林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱蘭特已進入視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30分鐘後到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更換攜帶的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.14,0:07:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要加厚盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你模仿純子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以態度有點傲慢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看不起我們\N這些職業機師吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也注重合作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是V2性能卓越罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好答案，\N那麽說回剛才的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.29,0:07:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和美愛娜\N誰是美麗的姐姐呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個也美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問誰美麗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.77,0:07:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索犯了錯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.24,0:07:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.24,0:07:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太遲鈍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是教訓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教訓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎？胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被美麗的姐姐戲弄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是笑的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅！ 你回來喇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.23,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡魯曼，他又聼到鈴聲吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.76,0:08:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎，華倫和卡里路呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在準備白色方舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.70,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去換衫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被戲弄得很可憐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我來艦橋有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡得很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.09,0:08:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這細路真的能代替雷達嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他有在\N卡沙尼里亞時的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.73,0:08:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.16,0:08:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在剛才的戰鬥中怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.33,0:08:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平時無分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.33,0:08:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米高，靠去凱蘭特的内側！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒他了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，好像沒吵醒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聼聞你被\N富蘭尼和美愛娜教訓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們很溫柔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.76,0:09:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要進入凱蘭特了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.86,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，可以讓我參觀嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新類型人嗎，無問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去前面的窗口看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.87,0:09:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些光是甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍艦！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有戰艦級！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是旗艦嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.79,0:10:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，神聖軍事同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已邀得聯邦軍幫手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.73,0:10:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的占撒哈林\N叫他們來這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的占.撒哈林…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣鎖解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.26,0:11:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，聼聞是協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神聖軍事同盟的珍路.達古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.53,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.97,0:11:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索.艾賓嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.00,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.88,0:11:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的經歷我聼過了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…？爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的經歷我聼過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看來很辛苦啊，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.12,0:11:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你為何會在這種地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直在找尋肯協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.87,0:11:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神聖軍事同盟作戰的\N聯邦軍部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.54,0:11:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在…卡沙尼里亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替媽媽築了墳墓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.59,0:12:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經常是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今已太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已變成這樣了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我已盡了全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的力量不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.44,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽真的很喜歡卡沙尼里亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你已把她\N葬在卡沙尼里亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.71,0:12:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也沒有遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，你也成長為一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.55,0:12:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我們想像中\N更利害的男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會叫你明白我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但身為遊擊隊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.62,0:12:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到正規軍的協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣做不是多餘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.10,0:12:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也收到媽媽的通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.24,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你就是V1的機師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.81,0:13:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們以前想把\N我教育成這樣吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎會呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你變成那樣和我無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也無勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣戴帽，帽會跌下來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.76,0:13:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是莎蒂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長大了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.43,0:13:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久無見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們就是白色方舟的乘員呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的事我好清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是奧迪羅.亨利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱蘭特的各位要回家一趟嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時間的話我們會去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們以前是匆忙\N離開凱蘭特的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,占.撒哈林大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆巴勒司令等人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.02,0:13:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正等待連賀斯Jr的乘員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了，我們立即來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好威風呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這是工作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有型呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯Jr已進入凱蘭特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的贊歷古有點不妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後的拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.54,0:14:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.64,0:14:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個大命的花娜！ 真可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個險些\N被斷頭台殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達斯羅被委任為艦隊指揮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只會成為卡格持的傀儡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我就不同啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了自己的命譽而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達斯羅保護的 [凱羅天使]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我遲早也會得到手的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，為了那個目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們能消滅眼前的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也就能\N快點接近卡格持了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊歷古的測試如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.04,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.77,0:15:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神聖軍事同盟\N已被趕入凱蘭特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比列騰會幫我\N消滅凱蘭特艦隊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.88,0:15:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來時也發出那命令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小子很生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞞着卡格持叫你來的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.89,0:15:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使這個凱羅天使完成了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不可說出來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫凱羅天使的巨大東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以產生精神或\N腦波控制的功用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.24,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該叫\N[精神感應] 的功用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，它完成後的實際威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.41,0:15:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些資料是神聖軍事同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.62,0:15:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作了很多犧牲後得回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.92,0:16:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望聯邦軍的各位知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中央政府…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個凱羅天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是戴在天使頭上的光環呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.00,0:16:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在叫名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯馬殊.馬沙歷、\N奧迪羅.亨利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索.艾賓，\N以上的人跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.87,0:16:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要趕我們走嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從第二扇門入去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎，入來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是我剛才介紹的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們來前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是和哥美斯上尉等人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.19,0:16:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直戰鬥\N到現在的最年輕機師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們叫我趁今日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你們編入正規軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.70,0:16:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.93,0:16:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來，少年兵並不罕見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你們的表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.87,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰是V2的機師胡索？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新類型人！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.81,0:17:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.98,0:17:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不安我好明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我會保証他的實際成績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，擊墜數目有多少？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擊墜數目？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.56,0:17:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10部，15部，\N或者更少…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10部也很利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是他的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是V1和V2利害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！ 但那也很利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，不會有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.68,0:17:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只媽媽是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也和\N卡沙尼里亞時完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索.艾賓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即就會進入艦隊戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.79,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.82,0:17:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯馬殊和奧迪羅的布拉斯達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和白色方舟一起留在後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.16,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便測試V2的米加雷射砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去支援艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫助神聖軍事同盟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍精銳部隊\N正集合在凱蘭特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消滅他們的人我保証會升級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫助神聖軍事同盟的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.79,0:18:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要消滅它們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！ 艦隊出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體馬上進入第一戰鬥準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟部隊被視為巡洋艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.22,0:18:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.93,0:18:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看正規軍的\N機動戰士戰吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米加雷射砲只是為了測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而放在後方支援嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.80,0:19:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們利用太陽電池的反射光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.59,0:19:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令敵人看不見我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.93,0:19:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備艦隊戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.97,0:19:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，胡索，\N向敵人機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射米加雷射砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,效果很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能使用吧，開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的動作很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備360度對空戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是北面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機從南面攻過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍的人在做甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟要使用米加粒子砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯馬殊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人想先來毀滅白色方舟嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,華倫，怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現了！ 發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是車胎型機動戰士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.59,0:20:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！ ？ 目標是艦隊嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道艦隊的\N數目有這麽多！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.76,0:20:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的聯邦軍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和神聖軍事同盟聯手了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會讓你們來嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.64,0:20:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要消滅旗艦就行了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.01,0:20:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個細路嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧！ 細路！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,細路！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…胡索操縱的…V2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他能生存到今日…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是靠那種力量嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不只是機動戰士的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果13嵗就能\N戰鬥到那個地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無…無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢說他是我的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是神聖\N軍事同盟偉大的軍力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.66,0:21:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你對他好一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.86,0:21:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.33,0:21:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種力量就不能發揮出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.23,0:21:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然，我身為爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.74,0:21:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士戰就由我來教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.51,0:22:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在銀色的海上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.45,0:22:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灼熱的波浪湧上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.25,0:22:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到跪下的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.13,0:22:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有變成說話，\N只是你的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.54,0:23:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能變得優美就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.48,0:23:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次TENDERNESS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.54,0:23:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的内心在月亮的菱鏡上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.75,0:23:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着閃耀的未來在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.45,0:23:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再次和你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.83,0:23:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你的瞳孔顯出孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.44,0:23:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到胡索爸爸的支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.81,0:23:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們向卑斯柏的艦隊進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.91,0:23:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索在意花娜\N和達斯羅的動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.91,0:23:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，露比.施羅小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.65,0:23:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕攻擊亦步步進迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.65,0:23:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索想避開她接近比列騰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.26,0:23:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回，機動戰士V高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.26,0:23:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮮血在光的漩渦裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.46,0:23:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請收看吧
